    // https://github.com/ethereum/solidity/issues/1290 is solved

        ConfigMaskDummy0,
        ConfigMarketTypeIsStrikedMask, // = 1
        ConfigMaskDummy2,
        ConfigMaskDummy3,
        ConfigIntervalTypeIsUsedMask // = 4

    enum SettlementType {
        FINAL, // = 0
        PRELIMINARY_FIRST // = 1
        //PRELIMINARY_MAX // = 65535

    enum MarketInterval {
        NONE, // = 0
        // the following constants are just proposed assignments
        YEARLY, // = 1
        QUATERLY, // 2
        MONTHLY, // = 3
        WEEKLY, // = 4
        DAILY, // = 5
        HOURLY, // = 6
        SHORT_TERM // = 7
    }

}
